---
title: Vietnamese-Style Beef Strips with Coconut Rice & Quick Pickled Onion
description: Zesty lemon lends its bright citrus flavour to quick-cooking beef strips in this stir-fry. Add rich coconut rice, colourful veggies and zingy pickled onion for a combination that turns a simple weeknight dinner into a feast of flavours.

*Unfortunately, this week's green beans were in short supply, so we've replaced them with broccoli. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
